description: Crab House and Soul Food mobile truck is known for great service and amazing garlic crab. What started as a small restaurant in Jacksonville, Florida has expanded to the food truck world. Bringing some of the best soul food dishes all over town. Satisfy your seafood need with a perfect combination plate of garlic season crab and shrimp one of the many top seller. Don't think twice about trying Crab House and Soul Food. It's food that speaks for itself!
name: Lewey's Crab House & Soul Food
